{"tid":2336832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港愛情故事 - 聖誕節","createTime":"2020-12-23T01:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T01:31:16.000Z","uid":190263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2938a9737bd0c7cf9dc980fbda9869bcf50969ea","tid":2336832,"uid":190263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:31:16.000Z","msg":"男：你聖誕有冇人約呀？<br />\n女：無呀，等緊人約囉。<br />\n男：咁就好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女：咁你想帶我去邊？<br />\n男：唔係呀，我睇吓係咪得我一個無人約。原來你都無人約，咁我都無咁慘。拜拜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biqMDL9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiqMDL9.jpg&h=262da906&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}